{"tid":1774321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"激罕！乃木坂46  生田絵理花眼鏡look","createTime":"2019-12-08T07:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T07:53:02.000Z","uid":63229,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdff8b8df6d717c175e41940d2f7d7268517bf2","tid":1774321,"uid":63229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"【#和你行 不反已出，12.8 維園見！】<br />\n<br />\n民陣 12.8 國際人權日遊行已取得警方不反對通知書，是 7.21 以來首次遊行獲批&mdash;&mdash; 8.18 變成「流水式集會」，8.31、10.1、10.20 幾次遊行申請皆被禁止。今次遊行也將是區議會選舉、人權法案通過後，最大的機會向國際社會表達香港人對抗警暴、爭取民主的決心。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，星期日 3 點，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n不反對通知書時間：<br />\n維園中央草坪｜12-6 PM<br />\n遊行路線｜3-10 PM<br />\n<br />\n【民陣 12.8 海報下載】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3890JqO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3890JqO&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7EkcwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=584d857f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3890JqO</a><br />\n【巴丟草為 12.8 遊行設計的海報】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2r5bSZj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r5bSZj&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7EkcwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=d1869153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2r5bSZj</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n守護香港．和你同行｜12.8 國際人權日遊行<br />\nStand With Hong Kong, Walk With You All:<br />\nHuman Rights Day Rally 2019<br />\n<br />\n12.8 星期日 Sunday｜3PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n#守護香港  #和你同行<br />\n#五大訴求 #缺一不可<br />\n#StandUp4HumanRights<br />\n#StandWithHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogfU8po.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogfU8po.jpg&h=b0bd5881&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27d9215160c8b4df520de2c2241270c2b1c05de1","tid":1774321,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"未上車就盡量黨鐵 狗封左好多過海隧道附近